{"id": 3051, "genre": 1000, "title": "你觉得自己在哪些方面可以算是一个「数字游牧民族」？", "description": "数字游牧民族，即，「能通过互联网创造收入、并不需要固定在同一个地方生活」的一群人。（题图来自：iStock ©️ elenabs）", "record_count": 2746, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20191106234019bG6NBnMo0mVihwWc.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-11-06T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 6017, "title": "你觉得自己在哪些方面可以算是一个「数字游牧民族」？", "content": "在当代你都是如何扮演一个“数字游牧民族”的？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 349163, "content": " 随时带着手机，电子产品变成身体的外接设备", "image": "img/option/option/20191106234955HRxAZ12yslaMbGu5.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349164, "content": "拥有很多互相独立的线上大本营（网站/app/社区）", "image": "img/option/option/201911062352232sJmGDwj7uVxWqtd.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349166, "content": "相对现实生活，对不需要实体的数字世界更有归属感", "image": "img/option/option/20191107000734riDxR9WcgVMjPIAf.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349167, "content": "大部分数字资产都可以浓缩到一个盘里，随身带走", "image": "img/option/option/20191107000906ZHBtyL8OhpPx4GaW.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349168, "content": "工作变成可携带模式，固定工作场所其实不是必要的", "image": "img/option/option/20191107001458M3LbvWRsBIAGiucT.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349169, "content": "不管是线上还是线下，其实都没有真正固定的“栖息地”", "image": "img/option/option/20191107001840hdNBHLX1crzRT7M4.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349171, "content": "不仅生活需要网络，相当一部分收入也来自互联网", "image": "img/option/option/20191107000551yuxjrH8V7NlWYg1B.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349172, "content": "并不太追求所谓的“稳定”，喜欢规划各种人生 plan B", "image": "img/option/option/20191107000333fOBtD2asl7h9Zi31.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349173, "content": "都没有，我不太符合", "image": "img/option/option/20191107000112dC5Jf7OmXDNxek0a.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}